window.bookSummaryJSON = "<i><p>\"Once I saw her, leaning over the balcony railing. I stopped the taxi and waved to her. She waved back, smiling like the sun breaking through clouds.\" </p></i><p><i></i>Suffused with warmth and passion, the stories in <i>Falling in Love Again</i> showcase the myriad variations of romantic love - fleeting, intimate, joyous, heartbreaking. Featuring classic stories by Ruskin Bond, such as 'The Eyes Have It' and 'The Girl from Copenhagen', this stirring collection captures the range of feelings that are indubitably part of the infinite spectrum of love. </p>"; 
